{"tid":1639612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 《榮光》歸香港 Apple再上架 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T11:40:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c08e6cd2199732d1b95e1f396cd07942af3b4394","tid":1639612,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191008/20783165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F20783165&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=5467366d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F20783165&h=d47bdd11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191008/20783165</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n《榮光》歸香港 Apple再上架 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191008/large/1570468084_a4ab.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191008%2Flarge%2F1570468084_a4ab.gif&h=0d10e591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》（圖）成為香港反送中抗爭代表歌曲，仲喺多個網上音樂平台正式上架，不過早排《榮光》忽然被香港Apple Music下架，但其他地區嘅Apple Music就冇，令好多網民質疑係咪俾Apple「河蟹」，不過Apple早前否認係佢哋嘅問題，而《榮光》嘅創作團隊就話處理中，相信好快會再上架，結果日前香港Apple Music終於又再出現返呢首歌。其實好多網民見香港Apple Music唔見咗首歌，紛紛去未下架嘅台灣、日本iTune Store買咗《榮光》，怕即使香港再出現返，唔知幾時又會唔見。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 家長回條加料 不同意禁罩 (李八方)"},{"pid":"2d1de6ea6914850815fb6a115da7f42caa0ac552","tid":1639612,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"疑 我都未知上返架  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實唔關apple事"},{"pid":"62bfdc3281adacb4afc3428498f1f58b5f35cc77","tid":1639612,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d1de6ea6914850815fb6a115da7f42caa0ac552","tid":1639612,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"疑 我都未知上返架  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實唔關apple事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:40:53.000Z","msg":"係仲未  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}